		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+150" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">The bar chart depicts world population growth [1] 1804 and shows the predicted world population [2] 2050. The table compares the distribution of the global population between more and less developed parts of the world in 2001 and 2050.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
